title: Bach, JS - Goldberg Variations - Schiff
description:
Bach's Goldberg Variations.

Johann Sebastian Bach's Goldberg Variations performed on piano by Andras Schiff and released by Decca in 1983. Now when it comes to piano versions of this work, I love Gould and Tureck's as much as the next guy, but you really must hear this version; it is about as good as you can possibly imagine.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
